Return type
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Upon failure, an empty table.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Upon success, a table with one row, and as many columns as there are aggregate
 functions in the query.
 The column types are all 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
